        Creates an instance for graph which initializes the vertex locations using initializer and sets the layoutSize of the layout to layoutSize.
        Parameters:
        graph - the graph on which the layout algorithm is to operate
        initializer - specifies the starting positions of the vertices
        layoutSize - the dimensions of the region in which the layout algorithm will place vertices
